<td colspan="2"><b>2000.08.06</b>: This is pretty much all we have in CVS: new
message browser, improved address book handling, more reliable mailbox
backend, alias expansion. The code has however some experimental and unfinished
features enabled so be warned! The POP problems some people
experienced have not been really addressed yet.</p>
